{"tid":2163120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"番歸喇 垃圾 u汪bk香討先係你龜宿","createTime":"2020-08-18T13:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T19:32:28.000Z","uid":359022,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"647a9cf852d9b0de05bac26861a8b0d82cbe3e8f","tid":2163120,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRxQv1V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRxQv1V.png&h=9a057e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個個都係嘴巴了得 不饒人 <br />\n又話最好有投票 有民意授權<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">真正記得今日開始有得投票嘅有幾多個</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n有自己想法、立場，唔該行動喇；推動投票啦連登仔，你係真連登仔嘅話。唔係，番歸u汪bk香討，呢度真適合你咩？</span><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n！！！！！！<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">大家做咗 香港民研 PORI 對立法會議員留任+健康碼嘅調查未呢</span></span></strong>！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161116</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"large\">早前已經登記咗嘅，應該已經收到email，請check。<br />\n未登記做調查羣組嘅，</span></strong></span>click here： https://<strong><span class=\"large\"><a href=\"http://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=a40d88cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<blockquote>即是咁，<br />\n你班泛民究竟諗住販民販多幾耐？<br />\n留任一個人大繞過香港法律程序宣佈繼續多一年嘅議會？<br />\n仲好聲氣同人話自己係入去「留守」？<br />\n留守啲咩？留守人大嘅sovereignty？<br />\n<br />\n你係投機做opportunists嘅，咪學蟲泰咁做到足囉，<br />\n忠誠地投下你神聖而冇傷害力嘅反對票，做個對北京有用嘅controlled opposition，<br />\n而家又要做雞，又要貞節牌坊，想點？<br />\n真係我的香港，my Hong Kong, my goodness！<br />\n<br />\n既然個別支持「留守」嘅泛民認爲佢哋嘅做法係「尊重民意」，<br />\n咁各位香港人係咪應該努力做下 香港民研 PORI 對立法會議員留任嘅調查呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「民調完，然後呢？」<br />\n喺柏拉圖嘅最理想領域，當然係成班臨立會議員入去開會，然後鎖門，放火，清潔我哋嘅香港。<br />\n但係唔係存在喺理想嘅領域，所以爲有朝著理想進發，向新香港邁進。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\ncredits to 高學歷廢青"},{"pid":"ed6b533e9fbc4556ad63ba0b8aea3cae532898a5","tid":2163120,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d11589fe1912882205679c1357ecd43754c6ae4","tid":2163120,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"！！！！！！<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">大家做咗 香港民研 PORI 對立法會議員留任+健康碼嘅調查未呢</span></span></strong>！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"large\">早前已經登記咗嘅，應該已經收到email，請check。<br />\n未登記做調查羣組嘅，</span></strong></span>click here： https://<strong><span class=\"large\"><a href=\"http://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=a40d88cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3b27d631d62a63145fc1084f94cfadb4969f1f73","tid":2163120,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042d7a29410ec8b88b5a26219a3ea9f905459ecc","tid":2163120,"uid":137265,"lik