n></span></strong>！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161116</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"large\">早前已經登記咗嘅，應該已經收到email，請check。<br />\n未登記做調查羣組嘅，</span></strong></span>click here： https://<strong><span class=\"large\"><a href=\"http://www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fhkpop-panel&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5gp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=a40d88cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.pori.hk/hkpop-panel</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<blockquote>即是咁，<br />\n你班泛民究竟諗住販民販多幾耐？<br />\n留任一個人大繞過香港法律程序宣佈繼續多一年嘅議會？<br />\n仲好聲氣同人話自己係入去「留守」？<br />\n留守啲咩？留守人大嘅sovereignty？<br />\n<br />\n你係投機做opportunists嘅，咪學蟲泰咁做到足囉，<br />\n忠誠地投下你神聖而冇傷害力嘅反對票，做個對北京有用嘅controlled opposition，<br />\n而家又要做雞，又要貞節牌坊，想點？<br />\n真係我的香港，my Hong Kong, my goodness！<br />\n<br />\n既然個別支持「留守」嘅泛民認爲佢哋嘅做法係「尊重民意」，<br />\n咁各位香港人係咪應該努力做下 香港民研 PORI 對立法會議員留任嘅調查呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「民調完，然後呢？」<br />\n喺柏拉圖嘅最理想領域，當然係成班臨立會議員入去開會，然後鎖門，放火，清潔我哋嘅香港。<br />\n但係唔係存在喺理想嘅領域，所以爲有朝著理想進發，向新香港邁進。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\ncredits to 高學歷廢青"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60a7b7526650ca77552d57b8fe364c6f6146bf6","tid":2163120,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1bf785cc33a89d46f7f777b61f70ef3d9be1ad","tid":2163120,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"931e751d70d13e2277413a2904e06f184a